OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Nigerian atheist has been sentenced  
OL,6, to 24 years in prison by a high court  
OL,7, in the northern state of Kano after    
OL,8, being convicted of blaspheming Islam.  
OL,10,FMubarak Bala, the 37-year-old president
OL,11,Fof the Humanist Association of Nigeria,
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to all 18 charges and   
OL,13,Fasked for leniency.                    
OL,15,FHe has been in detention since 2020.   
OL,17,FA group of Muslims had filed a petition
OL,18,Fto the authorities accusing Bala of    
OL,19,Fposting uncomplimentary messages about 
OL,20,FIslam on social media.                 
